channel.title: Quick way to edit 718 cache?
channel.description:
Hello and thank you for taking time to look into this. I only need someone to explain me wich cache editor i should use and how it works i really need to start working on my shops and where they are placed. I cant do so if i cant edit the cache. Please help me out.
Regards.

item.title: Quick way to edit 718 cache?
item.dc:creator: @Potzon Potzon
item.description:
@Potzon wrote:

You don’t need a cache editor to edit your shops.
If you’re using a 718 source, change the items in unpackedShops(.txt).

Read full topic
